{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-compound-finals/task-7","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Slušao sam zvukove i vežbao izgovaranje složenog nastavka i slogova.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"zh-a1-learn-compound-finals","challengeType":24,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Da bi izgovorio završetak mešavine <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ao</span>, počnite sa otvorenim ustima sa zvukom <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span>, zatim polako pomerite jezik i usne ka poziciji <span class=\"highlighted-text\">o</span>.</p>\n<p>Reakcija treba da bude glatka, bez prekida između ta dva zvuka. <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span> se naglašava na malo duže vreme, dok je <span class=\"highlighted-text\">o</span> kratko i lagano, što izaziva prirodan prelaz umesto dve različite samoglasnike.</p>\n<p>Kada <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ao</span> je praćeno početnim konsonantima, dobija slogove kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">bao</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">dao</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">gao</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">kao</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">zao</span>, i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">chao</span>.</p>\n<p>Da vežbamo izgovor ovih slogova, pa koristi <span class=\"highlighted-text\">zao</span> u različitim tonovima kao primer.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Pinyin</th>\n<th>Slova</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">zāo</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">遭</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">záo</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">凿</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">zǎo</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">早</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">zào</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">造</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-compound-finals/task-7"},"questions":[],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-center.png","characters":[{"character":"Lin Yating","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ZH_A1_pinyin_compound_finals.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":112.68,"finishTimestamp":136.09},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":1.89,"dialogue":{"text":"ao","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":2.93,"finishTime":3.79,"dialogue":{"text":"bao","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":5.06,"finishTime":5.89,"dialogue":{"text":"dao","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":7.18,"finishTime":8.12,"dialogue":{"text":"gao","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":9.65,"finishTime":10.62,"dialogue":{"text":"kao","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":12.17,"finishTime":13.16,"dialogue":{"text":"zao","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":14.57,"finishTime":15.58,"dialogue":{"text":"chao","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":17.52,"finishTime":18.33,"dialogue":{"text":"zāo","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":19.66,"finishT